text: DXJT (99.3 FM), simply known on-air as 99.3 FM, is a radio station owned and operated by the Joint Task Force Sulu. The station's studio is located in Camp Asturias, Brgy. Asturias, Jolo, Sulu.So long Romy Reyes: singer, peacemaker ==References== Category:Radio stations in Sulu Category:Radio stations established in 2017
title: DXJT
